// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0120 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: aac08bdf-44ef-553f-b31e-5f1bda11525a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*")
